<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p align="center">齐心抗“疫“，才有山河无恙，</p>
<p align="center">举国同心，方能共享盛世团圆，</p>
<p align="center">让我们记住这些面孔，</p>
<p align="center">记住这段刻骨铭心的岁月！</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201001/c913ea7c45214260b24282192f55403d.png" /></p>
<p>出品：汪金福、陈凯星、周亮、唐卫彬</p>
